criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients of any age with diagnosis of usual acinar adenocarcinoma of the prostate;

          2. Patients that treatment with HIFU is an option;

          3. And, that they accept to undergo the pre-and post-HIFU anorectal manometry;

          4. And, answer the questionnaires applied;

          5. And, signature of the informed consent form.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients who have no indication of HIFU treatment;

          2. Or, who have already undergone some anorectal surgery;

          3. Or, that they present some psychoneurological disease;

          4. Or, who have anatomical, functional or pathological alterations of the rectum or anal;
